MasterChef Australia Series 3 Episode 62

This week the contestants head to the Big Apple, the City That Never Sleeps, the culinary heartland that is New York! Don't miss a second as the top eight cook up a storm in the world's most famous city! On the second day, with one contestant in lock-down until the elimination at the end of the week, the other contestants undertake a major challenge.

Enjoy!
